-- Russia Central Bank Mulls Deposit Insurance Rise: Vedomosti Says
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-09-27T04:40:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-27/russia-central-bank-mulls-deposit-insurance-rise-vedomosti-says.html
Russia ’s central bank and  Finance
Ministry  are putting together a proposal to raise deposit
insurance from 700,000 rubles to 1 million rubles,  Vedomosti 
reported, citing a Finance Ministry employee.  OAO Sberbank, Russia’s biggest lender, is against an
increase, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
